    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or ding to be found! I've absolutely babied this car from day one, and it still has that fresh smell and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for absolute perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
