    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its stunning factory finish. The exterior is absolutely flawless, with deep, mirror-like paint and not a single stone chip, door ding, or swirl mark to be found. The alloy wheels are pristine, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero signs of bolster wear, the carpets are protected by original mats, and the dashboard remains free of any UV fading. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history and an engine bay so clean you could eat off it. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, collector-quality example that satisfies even the most discerning automotive enthusiast. It needs nothing but a new garage to call home.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
